snippet.title: Phantom Blade: Executioner TGS Trailer 2021
snippet.description:
The trailer for the newest entry in the Phantom Blade series - Phantom Blade: Executioner - shown at Tokyo Game Show 2021. English subtitles.

Let us know what you think! If you enjoy it and want to support the channel, don’t forget to subscribe and watch more TGS. Thank you!

#phantomblade #tgs #tokyogameshow
